Package org.encog.neural.neat

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NEATGenomeFactory
    This interface defines additional methods defined to create NEAT genomes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FactorNEATGenome
    This factory is used to create NEATGenomes.
    NEATCODEC
    This CODEC is used to create phenomes (NEATNetwork) objects using a genome (NEATGenome).
    NEATLink
    Implements a link between two NEAT neurons.
    NEATNetwork
    NEAT networks relieve the programmer of the need to define the hidden layer structure of the neural network.
    NEATPopulation
    A population for a NEAT or HyperNEAT system.
    NEATUtil
    NEAT does not make use of a special trainer.
    PersistNEATPopulation
    Persist a NEAT or HyperNEAT network.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    NEATNeuronType
    The types of neurons supported by NEAT.
